properties.name: Crome
properties.description: Posted by Rwalkerg 2815 S Shepherd Dr, Houston, 77098 This place was pretty cool, but super expensive. We had a large group and got there early. Good thing too, because it gets packed! Strength lies in numbers, so we were able to stake out some places at the bar and dance floor. The mix was awesome, playing old school stuff up to new music - all into a great dance mix. Its a smoke free bar - so it made it nice to not smell horrible when you are stumbling out at 2am. Super expensive drinks - go with a rich friend (or a generous one), but they are at least strong.

properties.name: Opus
properties.description: Posted by Rwalkerg412 Main St Houston, TX 770023 level club. Good place to dress up slutty and have a great time. Mid-priced drinks. Dance mix varies. Some nights they played awesome stuff, other nights was all techno. I like the techno included in a mix, or apart of a concert, but all house gets boring. Fairly large dance floor. We always go as a big group and lounge around on the top floor in the back. This place recently has gone downhill.
